    ## `o-` Object
    
    format: `.o-object-name[<element>|<modifier>]{}`
    
    Purely structural aspects of a UI, that are repetitive, shared, and used in any number of unrelated contexts    
    
    ```bash
    app/lib/styles/objects
    ├── _grid.styl
    ├── _spacing.styl
    ├── _wrapper.styl
    └── index.styl
    ```

