    ```stylus
    $spacing ?= 1.5em

    .o-wrapper {  
      padding-left $spacing
      padding-right $spacing

      &__full {
        padding-left 0
        padding-right 0
      }

      &__full, &__inverted {
        margin-left $spacing * -1
        margin-right $spacing * -1
      }

      &__inverted {
        padding-left $spacing
        padding-right $spacing
      } 
    }
    ```